post_content.caption: 'He was ferociously independent': Senator recalls Joe Lieberman's legacy
post_content.description:
Sen. Richard Blumenthal, D-Conn., joins Morning Joe to discuss the life and legacy of his friend and colleague Sen. Joe Lieberman, who died Wednesday at the age of 82.
